NightViper:

NightViper was almost uncontious, His head lolled back one side of his fave 
was smashed in and was  bleeding energon, he continued to try and get his 
systems functioning even though one eye was lying back in the other feild. He 
screeched as his chest burst with an electric explosion, missile shrapnel was 
mixed in with his robotic organs, his snake skin was lying around him in 
shards. He knew better then to try and transform, but the nano system would 
no begin if he didn't... "N-n-n-nightV-v-I-perrrrr Terrrrrorize!" He screamed 
as hi changed... what lay against the tree was what some would describe as a 
"roadkill" The hood was gone shredded the snake face was skeletal down one 
side its eyes were blinded. The body itself was skinless, and almost zombie 
like. "Eeeeeraghhh!" He coiled himself into a knot and hugged against the 
tree as his entire body began sparking... Through the pain all he could think 
about was StarStorm, He let his snake tongue flick out and he went towrads 
the direction she last headed, but as soon as he began to slither another 
pulse of electricity went though him and his body went into stasis lock. 
"Ssstarssstorm....." He blacked out and lay silent.
